  "body": "Create a validator provider so the QBFT use a smart contract to retrieve to set of validators.\n\nRequirements\n* Retrieve the validators from the smart contract using eth_call by calling the getValidators function at a particular block height\n* Cache the validator results so reduce cost of calling the smart contract\n* Include the fork overrides from transitions so that validators can still be overridden\n* Config qbft in for the validator contract address\n* Use the validator contract when the config is present otherwise use existing voting mechanism",
